Fantasy Points/Game: Average fantasy points scored per game.
Passing Yards (Advanced): Total passing yards (may include advanced adjustments or air yards components).
Completion % (Advanced): Percentage of passes completed (advanced stat — may adjust for drops, throwaways, etc.).
Yards/Attempt (Advanced): Average passing yards per attempt (advanced calculation).
CPOE: Completion Percentage Over Expected (accuracy relative to expected completions based on throw difficulty).
Completions (Advanced): Total completed passes (advanced version, may adjust for specific situations).
Air Yards: Total distance (in yards) that all pass attempts traveled in the air (before catch).
Air Yards/Attempt: Average air yards per pass attempt.
Completions 10+ Yards: Number of completed passes that gained 10 or more yards.
Completions 20+ Yards: Number of completed passes that gained 20 or more yards.
Completions 30+ Yards: Number of completed passes that gained 30 or more yards.
Completions 40+ Yards: Number of completed passes that gained 40 or more yards.
Completions 50+ Yards: Number of completed passes that gained 50 or more yards.
Red Zone Attempts: Number of pass attempts made inside the opponent’s 20-yard line.
QB Rating: Quarterback rating (passer efficiency metric using completions, yards, TDs, INTs).
Pocket Time: Average time (in seconds) the QB spends in the pocket before releasing the ball or being pressured/sacked.
Sacks (Advanced): Total number of times the QB was sacked (advanced tracking).
pressure_to_sack: Ratio of pressures that resulted in a sack (measures QB’s ability to avoid sacks when pressured).
QB Hits/Knockdowns: Number of times the QB was hit or knocked down (but not necessarily sacked).
QB Hurries: Number of times the QB was hurried (forced to throw earlier than intended).
Blitzes Faced: Number of defensive blitzes the QB faced.
Poor Throws: Number of passes classified as poorly thrown (off-target).
Receiver Drops: Number of passes dropped by receivers.
Rushing TD: Total rushing touchdowns scored by the QB.
Rushing Yards: Total rushing yards gained by the QB.
Rushing Attempts: Total rushing attempts by the QB.
Games Played (Advanced): Number of games played (advanced tracking; may account for partial appearances).
pressures: Number of times the QB was pressured by defenders (includes hits, hurries, sacks).
